title: The Journal of Business of the University of Chicago

contents.note: JSTOR (full text also available for subscription or payment)

additional-note: The October 1953 issue was the last to use 'The Journal of Business of the University of Chicago' on the cover, but that title was still used in some inner pages of 1954 issues. Some early 1950s issues of this journal were renewed under the title 'Journal of Business'.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Felice Gollotti for copyright research on this title.
